{"tid":2377654,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"十大屋苑周末錄530組睇樓量, 創10周新高, 怕遲買會升，形成小陽春","createTime":"2021-01-23T19:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T18:59:16.000Z","uid":73269,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2114df4aa5ba16846ddd518da9dabedfd1822f0d","tid":2377654,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:36:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">創10周新高</span></span><br />\n正面消息多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕遲買樓價會升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國總統順利交接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中美關係有望改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小陽春局面已形成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中原地產十大屋苑本周末錄得530組睇樓預約，較上周升7.1%，睇樓量創10周新高。中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示，近日大市正面消息多，美國總統順利交接，中美關係有望改善，本港股市亦大升，增加入市信心，不少買家希望趕及於新年前入市，怕遲買樓價會升，小陽春局面已形成，一二手交投暢旺，料週末交投氣氛熱鬧。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2859958/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2859958%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Tai%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=9d580bb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2859958/</a>"},{"pid":"71418124bb5775f2eebcfd4597a989256b129b7d","tid":2377654,"uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:59:50.000Z","msg":"等推post"},{"pid":"ee733a59346ea6a996b81da4d419ecbb5517a74c","tid":2377654,"uid":357591,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:23:37.000Z",